data.description: Great Starter home! Situated on 1 acre of land this 2 bedroom, 1 full bath home features a living room with a fireplace, a kitchen with a center island and appliances and a dining room with a built in wall unit.  Property being sold ''As-Is'' with right to inspect. Seller will make no repairs. Seller will not pay for or provide survey. Seller and Listing agent make no representations or warranties. Buyer to perform own due diligence.
